OL,4,CFrench films show far too much smoking,
OL,5,Ccampaigners say
OL,6, French cinema is still addicted to
OL,7, showing smoking on screen, as a new
OL,8, study reveals the practice features in
OL,9, nearly all the country's films.
OL,11,FSmoking gets 2.6 minutes of screen time
OL,12,Fon average per film - the equivalent of
OL,13,Fsix adverts, the French League Against
OL,14,FCancer found.
OL,16,F"Tobacco remains quasi-ubiquitous in
OL,17,FFrench films," the League says.
OL,19,FIt argues the exposure glamorises
OL,20,Fsmoking and is calling for new measures
OL,21,Fto cut down the amount shown in movies.
